Tie-CheckVariables
==================

Tie::CheckVariables aims to simplify the checks of values. In many programs you
want a variable to get only integer values or email addresses. With Tie::CheckVariables
you don't have to check the value for each assignment.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Carp

